OL,3,CBristol budget cuts: What services
OL,4,Cwill you lose and which will cost you
OL,5,Cmore?
OL,7,FWith funding cuts on the horizon for
OL,8,FBristol City Council, here's a look at
OL,9,Fwhat that means for residents.
OL,11,FThe leader of Bristol City Council
OL,12,Fsaid he's resigned to having to make
OL,13,Fhuge cuts to services in the city.
OL,15,FCllr Tony Dyer, Bristol City Council
OL,16,Fleader, said: "None of us joined this
OL,17,Fchamber to make cuts. We are in a
OL,18,Fserious financial situation. We're
OL,19,Fmaking decisions now that really
OL,20,Fshould have been made years ago.
