OL,7,F"We are making those decisions in
OL,8,Forder to put ourselves into a position
OL,9,Fwhat we're much more financially
OL,10,Fsustainable moving forward, so we can
OL,11,Fstart to deliver the services and the
OL,12,Ffacilities that this city deserves."
OL,14,FWith a #52 million funding gap, every
OL,15,Fcouncil service is under review.
OL,17,F#17m worth of planned refurbishment of
OL,18,Fcouncil housing is on hold for at
