OL,7,FShaban Ali has lived in Barton House
OL,8,Ffor almost a decade.
OL,10,FHe says residents there and in other
OL,11,Fcouncil tower blocks have been
OL,12,Fforgotten.
OL,14,FHe said: "I understand the council is
OL,15,Fin a difficult situation, but we've
OL,16,Fbeen in difficult situations for how
OL,17,Flong now? But we need a respite
OL,18,Furgently, we need help."
