OL,7,FDrivers could be charged more to enter
OL,8,FBristol's Clean Air Zone (CAZ) under
OL,9,Fcouncil plans that would also see
OL,10,Fdisabled badge holders pay for parking.
OL,12,FThe current #9 daily fee has not been
OL,13,Fincreased since the scheme launched in
OL,14,F2022, and council officers are seeking
OL,15,Fapproval to ask the government for
OL,16,Fpermission to raise it in line with
OL,17,Finflation.
